<p> </p>
<p><strong><img src="http://www.edenhrconsulting.com/images/stories/our-people/ben-photo.jpg" alt="ben-photo" style="float: left; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px;" height="205" width="150" />Ben Pirt</strong></p>
<p><strong>Human Resources Advisor</strong></p>
<p>Ben has recently graduated with a BA (Hons) Human Resource Management from The University of Portsmouth. He is a generalist with an interest in L&D, Employment Relations and Employment Law.</p>
<p>Currently, Ben is working towards CIPD accreditation and his MSc. in Human Resource Development.</p>
<p>Ben undertakes a variety of ad-hoc administrational and HR project based work for Eden HR.</p>
<p>Ben is an RFU Tag qualified coach and referee, and enjoys voluntarily coaching in his spare time. He has previously worked in customer facing roles, such as outdoor events instruction and in PR for a national events company.</p>
